description:
Friday December 05, 2008.

Alex welcomes hip hop artist Paris from San Francisco. Other guests include Webster Tarpley, who will be in-studio and will discuss the election of Obama and the Mumbai false-flag attack, and the Health Ranger, Jeffrey Smith, who will address GMO foods and other health issues.

Hour-1: News then Webster Tarpley
Hour-2: Webster Tarpley then Paris
Hour-3: Paris then Jeffrey Smith
Hour-4: Jeffrey Smith then Webster Tarpley - Round 2
